public class MatrixClassGeneric<T> extends AbstractMatrixGeneric<T>

Title: MatrixClassGeneric

Description:

Generic matrix implementation which allows users to instantiate the class with any data type. Note that the current implementation only supports 2d matrices
Version:
1.0
Author:
Sam R. Thangiah
